text: "Eat the Rich" is a 1993 song by Aerosmith and is the second single form their 11th studio album Get a Grip. It went to number 34 in the United Kingdom and number 45 in Canada. It had success on rock radio stations in the United States. ==Track listing== ==Notes== Category:1993 songs Category:Hard rock songs Category:Aerosmith songs
